commitResults.messageTitle: Update Duke.java to comply with coding standard
Add three functionality for ToDos, Events, Deadlines
commitResults.messageBody:
Add classes Todo, Event, Deadline which inherits from the Task class. New commands (todo, event, deadline) allow addition of these specialized tasks.
The program is also more modular now.

commitResults.messageBody:
Now Duke supports the date command.
The date command searches for Deadlines and Events with the same date, and displays the result.
Fixed some bugs with the command parser discovered during the testing of dates.
